description: This file defines a lightweight navigation type ('Nav') intended for internal routing purposes within a React project. It acts as a compatibility shim, not using external routing libraries like react-navigation, and provides type definitions for navigation actions such as 'navigate' and optionally 'goBack'.

methods.name: navigate
methods.description: Function to navigate to a specified route ('Home', 'Game', or 'Settings').

methods.name: goBack
methods.description: Optional function to navigate back to the previous page.
